# appinspector
[![codecov](https://codecov.io/gh/codeskyblue/appinspector/graph/badge.svg?token=aLTg4VOyQH)](https://codecov.io/gh/codeskyblue/appinspector)

appinspector.devsleep.com client

Based on

- fastapi
- adbutils
- tidevice3

# DEVELOP
```bash
# install deps
pip install poetry
poetry install

# run server
make dev
```
